metadata.name: A sincere moment in time.
metadata.description:
Animation 
H.264 
2240x4200

Took some video I had of my family the other morning, and thought it would be interesting to see what would happen if I ran some of the frames through Google's Disco Diffusion v5.3. I trained it on the works of the fauvism movement from the early 1900s. Works including the likes of famous artists like Henri Matisse and Claude Monet.
